duties_responsibilities.duty: Lead and supervise Operations Associates to ensure safe and productive work, serving as the point of escalation for daily operations.
Receive and place products from vendors, prepare customer orders, and manage work area organization.
Ensure smooth delivery of customer orders, maintain menus and systems, and facilitate Dasher pickups.
Monitor supplier deliveries and manage cleaning and maintenance schedules to ensure facility functionality.
Contribute ideas to improve operations, quality, and customer experience.

education_certification.credential: High school diploma or GED equivalent
